import React from 'react'
import { Navbar, Container, Nav } from 'react-bootstrap'

const MyNavBar = () => {
    return (

        <Navbar expand="lg" >
            <Container>
                <Navbar.Brand href="/" className="text-light">SpIcE</Navbar.Brand>
                <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
                <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
                    <Nav className="me-auto">
                        <Nav.Link href="/music" className="text-light">Music</Nav.Link>
                        <Nav.Link href="/movies" className="text-light">Movies</Nav.Link>
                    </Nav>
                </Navbar.Collapse>
            </Container>
        </Navbar>

    )
}

export default MyNavBar
